{
  "doc_id": "50995",
  "text": "In [CITATION_1] the numerical investigation has been expanded into three dimensions thus exploring the orbital structure of the three degrees of freedom Earth-Moon system. Furthermore, very recently the escape and collision dynamics in the SaturnTitan and in the Pluto-Charon binary planetary systems have been revealed in [CITATION_2] and [CITATION_3] , respectively, by classifying initial conditions of orbits in the configuration space.",
